#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"Our actions have consequences. Some consequences happen naturally (“if you break something, you can’t use it anymore”). Other consequences we set as a family to motivate us to follow the rules (“if you come home late, you can’t go out with friends tomorrow”).\n"
"\n"
"HOW you set and use consequences together matters.\n"
"\n"
"Getting consequences right helps teens behave better and makes family life calmer."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje singeziphumo zokuzola.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Izenzo zethu zineziphumo. Ezinye iziphumo zenzeka ngokwendalo. (\"xa usophula into, awuphindi uyisebenzise nanini na \"). Ezinye iziphumo sizihlela silusapho ukukhuthazana ukulandela imigaqo (\"ukuba ubuyela ekhaya emva kwexesha, awuzuphuma nezihlobo ngomso\").\n"
"\n"
"Indlela obeka kunye nosebenzisa ngayo iziphumo zombini zibalulekile.\n"
"\n"
"Ukufumana imiphumela ngendlela eyiyo, kuncedisa umntana ofikisayo aziphathe ngcono kwaye kwenza nobomi bosapho buzole."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How will introducing calm consequences help you and your family? Play to learn more"
msgstr "Ingaba ukwazisa imiphumela yokuzola kuzakuncedisa njani wena nosapho lwakho? Dlala ukuze ufunde ngakumbi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"It is important that when we introduce consequences to our teenagers we involve them, but also important that we are calm when we introduce consequences.\n"
"\n"
"That will assist us to agree on introducing calm consequences to our teenagers, and our teenagers will easily remember them when they are involved and that will make them responsible."
msgstr ""
"Molweni, nonke. \n"
"\n"
"Umxholo wanamhlanje ungemiphumela ezolileyo.\n"
"\n"
"Kubalulekile ukuba sibabandakanye abantwana bethu abafikisayo xa sisazisa ngemiphumela, kodwa kukwabalulekile ukuzola xa sibazisa iziphumo.\n"
"\n"
"Oku kuza kusinceda sivumelane ekwaziseni imiphumela ezolileyo ebantwaneni bethu abafikisayo, kwaye abantwana bethu abafikisayo bayakukhumbula lula xa bebandakanywa kwaye lonto iza kwenza babe noxanduva."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Calm consequences work best when they are fair, agreed on together, and followed through consistently - not in anger."
msgstr "Iziphumo zomoya ophantsi zisebenza ngcono xa zinobulungisa, nivumelene nonke, zilandelwe ngokungajikajikiyo - kungekho msindo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_13.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Agreeing on consequences together works! Tap play to hear @data.characters.media_female_13.name tell her story"
msgstr "Ukuvumelana ngemiphumela ninonke kuyasebenza! Cofa udlala ukuva @data.characters.media_female_13.name exela ibali lakhe"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my teenagers did something to make me angry, I would shout at them and punish them right away. But the next time they did it again! I could not understand why they did not hear me even when I shouted.\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name helped me understand that my teenagers will listen to me more when I am calm. So, when something happens, I take a deep breath and say “we will talk about this later when we are both calm.”\n"
"\n"
"We even agree on the consequences together now before something goes wrong. This has worked wonders – I have seen a huge change in my teen’s behaviour now that they are more involved, and I have less stress.\n"
"\n"
"I wish I knew this long ago, but it is never too late to start!"
msgstr ""
"Xa abantwana bam abafikisayo benze into endenza ndibe nomsindo,bendibangxolisa, ndibohlwaye kwangoko. Kodwa xa bephinda ukuyenza! bendingayiqondi ukuba kutheni bengandiva noba sendibangxolisile.\n"
"@global.app_name indincedile ndaqonda ukuba abantwana bam abafikisayo bangamamela kakhulu xa ndinomoya ophantsi. Ngoko, xa kusenzeka into nditsala umoya ndithi \"sakuthetha ngayo ngelinye ixesha xa sinomoya ophantsi.\"\n"
"\n"
"Siye sivumelane kunye ngemiphumela ngoku ngaphambi ngokuba kwenzeke into engalunganga. Oku kwenze umangaliso-Ndibone umehluko omkhulu kwindlela yokuziphatha komntwana wam ofikisayo ngoba beyinxalenye, kwaye lwatsho lwehla uxinzelelo.\n"
"\n"
"Akwaba bendiyazile kwangaphambili, kodwa akuphelanga xesha lakuyiqala!"

