msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name did not let his son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, explain"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name akamvumelanga unyana wakhe,@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, acacise"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The consequence was not discussed beforehand with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"
msgstr "Imiphumela ayizange incokolwe kwangaphambili no @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The consequence was too strong"
msgstr "Umphumo ubungqongqo kakhulu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, a strong reaction like that just made everyone more angry and upset."
msgstr "Ewe, intsabelo erhabaxa ngolo hlobo yenze wonke umntu wanomsindo kakhulu waza wacaphuka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Teens often break rules. This is normal - growing up is a difficult time when they are learning about who they are.\n"
"\n"
"Luckily, there are ways to discipline without getting angry or using violence… and they work well!\n"
"\n"
"Giving calm consequences is important because it helps teens learn from their actions and take responsibility for their choices."
msgstr ""
"Abantwana abafikisayo bahlala beyaphula imigaqo. Oku kuqhelekile - ukukhula lixesha elinzima xa bezifunda ukuba bangoobani. \n"
"\n"
"Ngethamsanqa, zikhona iindlela zokohlwaya ngaphandle kokuba nomsindo okanye ukusebenzisa ubundlobongela… yaye zisebenza kakuhle!\n"
"\n"
"Ukunika imiphumela ezolileyo kubalulekile kuba kunceda abantwana abafikisayo bafunde kwizenzo zabo kwaye bathathe uxanduva ngezinto abazikhethela zona."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Imagine you are the parent and @data.characters.f1_son_18.name came home late. \n"
"What consequence would help here?"
msgstr ""
"Khawube nombono ukuba ubungumzali kwaye @data.characters.f1_son_18.name afike ekhaya emva kwexesha.\n"
"Yeyiphi imiphumela enokunceda apha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cannot play with phone the next day"
msgstr "Akanakudlala ngomnxeba kusuku olulandelayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That's right!\n"
"\n"
"And remember, consequences are not quite the same as punishment: they give our teens a chance to learn responsibility for their actions.\n"
"\n"
"And they are more controlled AND effective than hitting or shouting!"
msgstr ""
"Kulungile!\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye khumbula, imiphumela ayiye ifane ncam nesohlwayo: inika abantwana bethu abafikisayo ithuba lokuba bafunde uxanduva ngezenzo zabo.\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye bayalawuleka ngakumbi KWAYE isebenza ngakumbi kunokubetha okanye ukubangxolisa!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now imagine @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name fight over a phone. \n"
"What consequence would help here?"
msgstr ""
"Ngoku yibanombono @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name no @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name besilwa ngefowuni.\n"
"Yeyiphi imiphumela enokunceda apha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No gadget use the next day"
msgstr "Makungasetyenziswa sixhobo kusuku olulandelayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Write a letter of apology"
msgstr "Bhala ileta yokuxolisa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cannot see friends the next day"
msgstr "Akakwazi ukubona abahlobo bakhe ngosuku olulandelayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cannot play with phone after dinner (or next hour)"
msgstr "Aninakudlala ngefowuni emva kwedinala (okanye kwiyure elandelayo)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take 5 minutes' pause in a separate part of the room"
msgstr "Yima kangangemizuzu emi 5 kwigumbi elisecaleni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great idea! Calm consequences work best when they are fair, happen soon after the behaviour, and are used the same way each time. This helps your teen understand what to expect and gives them a clear chance to learn from their actions."
msgstr "Umbono omhle! Iziphumo zomoya ozolileyo zisebenza ngcono xa zinobulgisa, zisenzeka kwangoko emva kwendlela yokuziphatha, zisetyenziswe ngokungajika-jikiyo ngalo lonke ixesha. Oku kuncedisa ukuba umntwana wakho ofikisayo ukuba ukuqonde amakakulindele kwaye kubanike ithuba elicacileyo lokuba bafunde kwizenzo zabo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now imagine @data.characters.f2_son_15.name is helping with a special chore. \n"
"What consequence would help here?"
msgstr ""
"Ngoku yibanombono @data.characters.f2_son_15.name encedisa ngemisetyenzana ekhethekileyo.\n"
"Yeyiphi imiphumela enokunceda apha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra time with friends on weekend (1 hr)"
msgstr "Ixesha elithe chatha nabahlobo ngempelaveki (iyure e-1)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cooking teen's favourite meal"
msgstr "Ukupheka ukutya okuthandwa ngumntwana ofikisayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra time with phone after dinner (30 min)"
msgstr "Ixesha elithe chatha nefowuni emva kwedinala (imizuzu engama-30)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Watching teen's TV show together"
msgstr "Ukubukela kunye inkqubo yabantwana abafikisayo KUMABONAKUDE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra one-on-one time on Sunday (30 min)"
msgstr "Ixesha elongezelelkileyo lenu nobabini ngeCawa (imizuzu engama-30)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Wonderful! Positive consequences like this build trust and show your teen that helpful behaviour is noticed and appreciated. When rewards are fair, timely, and consistent, they motivate teens to keep making good choices and strengthen your bond too."
msgstr "Iyamangalisa! Iziphumo ezilungileyo ezifana nezi zakha ukuthembeka ziphinde zibonise umntwana wakho ofikisayo ukuba indlela yokuziphatha encedisayo iyaqatshelwe kwaye yamkelekile. Xa umvuzo unobulungisa, ngemaxesha onke, kwaye ingajikajiki, ikhuthaza abantwana abafikisayo baqhubeke besenza okulungileyo iphinde iqinise ubudlelwane benu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some tips to help you with calm consequences:"
msgstr "Nazi ezinye zeengcebiso ezinokunceda kwimiphumela ezolileyo:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "EXPLAIN"
msgstr "CACISA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Check you are both calm. Take a few breaths. Explain to your teen why you are concerned about their behaviour.\n"
"\n"
"Explain the reasons why the rule mattered. You can share your feelings – it is okay to say you are disappointed."
msgstr ""
"Qiniseka ukuba nobabini nizolile. Tsala umoya izihlandlo ezimbalwa. Cacisela umntwana wakho ofikisayo ukuba kutheni ukhathazwe sisimilo sakhe.\n"
"\n"
"Cacisa izizathu zokuba kutheni lo mgaqo ubalulekile. Ningabelana ngemvakalelo zenu - kulungile ukutsho ukuba uphoxekile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How you introduce calm consequences is important. When you involve your teen, things usually go better!"
msgstr "Indlela owazisa ngayo imiphumela ezolileyo ibalulekile. Xa ubandakanya umntwana wakho ofikisayo, izinto zibangcono!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "AGREE"
msgstr "VUMA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Plan consequences with your teen for following and not following the rule.\n"
"\n"
"Ask for their ideas. Talk until you agree on something realistic.\n"
"\n"
"Make a consequence for NOT following the rule and a privilege when they DO follow the rule."
msgstr ""
"Ceba imiphumo nomntwana wakho ofikisayo yokuwulandela nokungawulandeli umgaqo.\n"
"\n"
"Cela ezakhe izimvo. Thethani de nivumelane ngento esengqiqweni.\n"
"\n"
"Yenza umphumo WOKUNGAWULANDELI umgaqo nengenelo yaxa eye WAWULANDELA umgaqo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, consequences are more successful if you discuss and agree in advance with teens before you apply them."
msgstr "Khumbula, imiphumela iyimpumelelo enkulu xa nibonisana nivumelane kwangethuba nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ngaphambi kokuba uyibeke."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "ACT"
msgstr "YENZA OKUTHILE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**When your teen follows the rule, give praise and privileges!** \n"
"They will feel respected and valued. Remember: The more we praise them, the more they will show that good behaviour!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**When your teen does not follow the rule, follow through with the consequence.** \n"
"When your teen breaks the rule, calmly give the consequence. This should be FAIR (not too harsh), IMMEDIATE (do it straight away), CONSISTENT (same every time)."
msgstr ""
"**Xa umtwana wakho ofikisayo elandela imigaqo, mncome umnike namalungelo.**\n"
"Bayakuziva behloniphekile kwaye bexabisekile. Khumbula: Xa siqubeka sibancoma, kuxa beqhubeka nokubonisa indlela elungileyo yokuziphatha.\n"
"\n"
"**Xa umntwana wakho engalandeli umgaqo, landela ngokwemiphumela**\n"
"Xa umntwana wakho esophula umgaqo, ngokuzolileyo mnike imiphumela. Kufanele ibenobulungisa (ungabiqatha),\n"
"NGOKONANGOKO (yenze ngokonangoko), INGAJIKAJIKI (ngohlobo olunye ngalo lonke ixesha)."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye incebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, you can also agree on GOOD consequences for GOOD actions to see more positive behaviour!"
msgstr "Khumbula, kananjalo ningavumelana ngziphumo EZILUNGILEYO ukwenzela izenzo EZILUNGILEYO ukuze ubone indlela entle yokuziphatha ngakumbi!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now let's go back to @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name:"
msgstr "Ngoku masibuyele emva ku @data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye notata wakhe, @data.characters.f1_father.name:"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am concerned that you are often still coming home late, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. What can we do to help you remember to come home in time?"
msgstr "Iyandixhalabisa into yokuhlala ubuya emva kwexesha ekhaya, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. Singenza ntoni ukukunceda ukuba ukhumbule ukubuya ekhaya kwangethuba?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If I come home in time, maybe I can stay up 30 minutes later than usual?"
msgstr "Ukuba ndibuyela ekhaya ngethuba mhlawumbi ndingakwazi ukuhlala imizuzu eyi 30 ngaphezulu kunesiqhelo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That is a good idea! And what should we do if you don’t follow the rule?"
msgstr "Ngumbono omhle lowo! Kwaye singenza ntoni xa ungalandeli umgaqo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "(mumbles) Mgmluuhm..."
msgstr "(mumbles) Mgmluuhm..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh come on, I know you have some ideas."
msgstr "Oh khawuze, ndiyayazi unayo eminye imibono."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay…. What about, I have to do my homework?"
msgstr "Kulungile…. Uthini nge, kufanele ndenze umsebenzi wasikolo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You have to do your homework anyway. If you forget the rule, is it fair that you will not be able to see your friends the next day?"
msgstr "Kufanele wenze umsebenzi wakho nakanjani. Ukuba uwulibele umgaqo, ingaba bubulungis ukuba ungababoni abahlobo bakho kusuku olulandelayo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name."
msgstr "Kulungile, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*The next day...*"
msgstr "* Kusuku olulandelayo...*"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name! What time is it! It is late!"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name! Ngubani ixesha ngoku! Kusemva kwexesha!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sorry @data.characters.f1_father.role_name – you can go back to sleep."
msgstr "Uxolo @data.characters.f1_father.role_name - ungahamba uyolala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is WAY past the time you were supposed to be home!"
msgstr "Lidlule KUDALA ixesha ebekufanele ubuye ngalo ekhaya!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I can explain, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, I can."
msgstr "Ndingacacisa @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, ndinako."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, it is the middle of the night and you came home later than we agreed. Whatever the reason is, you must understand that this is not acceptable. Your @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name and I felt really worried."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, kusezinzulwini zobusuku kwaye ubuyele ekhaya emva kwexesha ebesivumelene ngalo.Nokuba isizathu sithini, kufanele uqonde ukuba ayamkelekanga lonto.Umama wakho @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name kunye nam sizive sikhathazekile nyhani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My friends wanted me to stay longer. They were calling me a baby for having to go home already."
msgstr "Abahlobo bam bebefuna ndihlale ixesha elide, bebendibiza ngokuba ndingumntwana kuba kufuneke ndigodukile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I know it can be hard to say no to your friends. Let’s talk more about this in the morning when we have had some rest."
msgstr "Ndiyayazi ukuba kunganzima ukuthi hayi kubahlobo bakho. Masithethe ngakumbi ngalento kusasa xa siphumlile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sorry I worried you and @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."
msgstr "Ndicela uxolo ngokunikhathaza wena kunye no @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you. Now go to bed, but just to be clear, as you came home later than we agreed, you will not be allowed to go out tomorrow night."
msgstr "Enkosi. Ngoku hamba uyokulala, kodwa ukucacisa nje, njengokuba ubuyele ekhaya emva kwexesha besivumelene ngalo, awuzokuvumeleka ukuba uhambe ebusuku ngomso."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about this story."
msgstr "Makhe sicinge ngeli bali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why did using a consequence work well this time?"
msgstr "Kutheni ukusebenzisa umphumo kusebenze kakuhle kweli tyeli?"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name and his son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, discussed consequences when they were both calm"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name kunye nonyana wakhe@data.characters.f1_son_18.name baxoxa ngemiphumela xa bobabini bezolile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "They agreed on consequences together"
msgstr "Bavumelene bobabini ngemiphumo"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name responded calmly but firmly when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name broke the rule"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name uphendule zolileleyo kodwa egxininisa xa @data.characters.f1_son_18.name ophule umgaqo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name listened to his son"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name wamamela unyana wakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The consequence was realistic and appropriate"
msgstr "Umphumo ubusengqiqweni yaye ufanelekile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly! Consequences work best when they are set calmly, agreed on together, and followed through with care. By listening to your teen and staying firm but kind, you are correcting behaviour AND building trust and helping them learn responsibility."
msgstr "Nqo! Imiphumela isebenza ngcono xa ibekwa ngokuzolileyo, nivumelana kunye, kwaye ilandelwe ngenkathalo Ngokumamela umntwana wakho ofikisayo kwaye uhlale ugxininisa kodwa unobubele, ulungisa indlela yokuziphatha KWAYE wakha ukuthembana kunye nokumncenda ukufundeni uxanduva."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It is time to learn and practise!\n"
"\n"
"Plan a calm consequence for your teenagers arguing with each other during dinner."
msgstr ""
"Ngoku lixesha lokufunda nokuziqhelanisa.\n"
"\n"
"Cwangcisa imiphumela ezolileyo yabantwana bakho abafikisayo abaxambulisanayo ngexesha lesidlo sasebusuku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some ideas from other parents. Tap each behaviour to see an example of a fair consequence!"
msgstr "Nazi ezinye iimbono ezisuka kwabanye abazali. Cofa indlela nganye yokuziphatha ukuze ubone umzekelo wemiphumela enobulungisa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Behaviour: Coming home after the agreed time"
msgstr "Ukuziphatha kakubi: Ukubuyela ekhaya emva kwexesha ebesivumelene ngalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Consequence: Cannot see friends the next day."
msgstr "Imiphumela emibi: Awuzozibona izihlobo ngosuku olulandelayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Behaviour: Talking rudely"
msgstr "Ukuziphatha kakubi: Ukuthetha krwada"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Consequence: Write a letter of apology."
msgstr "Imiphumela emibi: Bhala imbalelwano yokuxolisa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Behaviour: Helping out with shopping"
msgstr "Ukuziphatha Kakuhle: Ukuncedisa ngokuyokuthenga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Consequence: 30 minutes extra doing an activity of their choice."
msgstr "Imiphumela emihle: imizuzu eyi 30 eyongezelelekileyo besenza imidlalo abazikhetheleyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Behaviour: Helping look after younger siblings"
msgstr "Ukuziphatha kakuhle: Ukuncedisa ekunakekela abantwana bakowenu abancinci"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Consequence: One hour of extra time with friends on the weekend."
msgstr "Imiphumela emihle: Iyure enye eyongezelelweyo yexesha kunye nabahlobo ngempela veki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now let's think more about negative consequences. Which of these consequences do you feel is appropriate?"
msgstr "Ngoku masicinge ngakumbi ngemiphumela emibi. Yeyiphi kulemiphumela oyiva ifanelekile?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not seeing any friends for a month"
msgstr "Ukungababoni abahlobo bam kangangenyanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This may be hard to do for you and also too harsh! \n"
"\n"
"Remember, consequences should be fair, immediate and consistent."
msgstr ""
"Lento inganzima ukuba uyenze kwaye ingangqwabalala!\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula, imiphumela ibengokufanelekileyo ngoko nangoko kwaye ingaguquguquki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cancelling their birthday plans in a month's time"
msgstr "Ukurhoxisa amulungiselelo osuku lakhe lokuzalwa kwixeshana nje lenyanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This is too far in the future and too harsh as well! \n"
"\n"
"Remember, consequences should be fair, immediate and consistent."
msgstr ""
"Oku kukude kakhulu kwixesha elizayo kwaye kunokubaqatha kwakhona!\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula, imiphumela ifanele ibenobulungisa, kwangoko kwaye ingaguquguquki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No TV this evening"
msgstr "Anizombukela UMABONAKUDE ngokuhlwanje"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Perfect, this sounds fair and can be done straight away."
msgstr "Kuhle, oku kuvakala kunobulungisa kwaye kungenzeka ngoko nangoko."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember, consequences should be:** \n"
"⚖️ FAIR (not too harsh) \n"
"💨 IMMEDIATE (do it straight away) \n"
"🎯 CONSISTENT (same every time)"
msgstr ""
"**Khumbula, imiphumela ingayi:** \n"
"⚖️ UBULUNGISA (ingabi qatha) \n"
"💨 Ngokonangoko (Yenze ngokonangoko) \n"
"🎯 UNGAJIKAJIKI (ifane ngalo lonke ixesha)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you agree on one NEGATIVE consequence and one POSITIVE consequence with your teen?"
msgstr "Ningavumelana kwisiphumo esinye ESIBI nakwe sinye ESIHLE nomntwana wakho ofikisayo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's fantastic! When teens help choose their own consequences - both positive and negative - they are more likely to understand and stick to them. You are helping them grow into a responsible young adult."
msgstr "Kuyamangalisa! Xa abantwana abafikisayo bezikhethela ngokwabo izphumo- ezihle nezimbi - bangakwazi ukuqonda kwaye bahlale bezibambile. Uyabanceda bakhule belulutsha oluthatha uxanduva."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s a great start! Take your time - you can come up with ideas together step by step."
msgstr "Sisiqalo esihle eso! Thatha ixesha lakho - ningeza nembono zenu kunye kancinci kancinci."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. These conversations can be tricky at first. Keep spending time together and try again when the moment feels right. You are already on the right path."
msgstr "Kulungile. Ezincoko zinganobuzaza ekuqaleni. Qhubekani nichitha ixesha kunye zamani kwakhona xa ithuba livuma. Sele nikwindlela entle."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When consequences are calm, clear, and agreed on together, teens are more likely to follow the rules. They will feel respected, not punished, and that is the best way to help our teens learn."
msgstr "Xa iziphumo zikumoya ozolileyo, nocacileyo, nibe nivumelene kunye, abantwana abafikisayo kubalula nokulandela imigaqo. Baya kuziva behloniphekile, bengohlwaywa, leyo yeyonandlela yokunceda abantwana abafikisayo bafunde."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_6.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how @data.characters.media_daughter_6.name learned to appreciate calm consequences"
msgstr "Cofa udlala ukumamela ukuba u@data.characters.media_daughter_6.name ufunde njani ukwamnkela iziphumo zomoya ophantsi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"My mom and dad would always punish me when they were angry with me. They would shout at me and I would also get angry. I often did not follow the rules, because they were too harsh, I did not understand what they were saying, or I would not even bother listening to them, because we were all angry.\n"
"\n"
"One day, they asked me: Let's think together what the consequence should be for not coming home in time. It was great to give my view – before something happens that makes us all angry. We are all calm and agree first. It is easier for me to follow the rules now because I know I agreed on the rule and on the consequence if I do not follow the rule."
msgstr ""
"Umama notata basoloko bendohlwaya xa ndibacaphukisile. Bayandingxolisa ndibenomsindo. Bendingasoloko ndiyilandela imigaqo, kuba basoloko bengqwabalala, ndingakuqondi oko bakuthethayo, okanye ndingazisokolisi nangokubamamela kuba bonke bacaphukile.\n"
"\n"
"Ngenye imini bandibuza: Makhe sicinge ngokuba zeziphi iziphumo esinokuzenza malunga nokungabuyi ekhaya ngexesha.\n"
"Bekukuhle ukuveza izimvo zam-ngaphambi kokuba kwenzeke into esenza sibe nomsindo sonke. Besinomoya ozolileyo sonke sagqiba kuqala. Kube lula kum ukulandela umgaqo ngoku kuba ndiyayazi ndivumile kumgaqo nakwiziphumo ukuba andiwulandeli umgaqo."

